  <section class="dd-section dd-section-mid">
    <div class="dd-container">
      <span class="dd-kicker">04. MACHINE CONFIGURATION</span>
      <h2 class="dd-h2">LZ-1325 CNC router configured for event decoration production.</h2>
      <p class="dd-copy">
        The final setup focused on stable material holding, printed panel processing, knife tooling, and real workshop operation.
      </p>

      <div class="dd-equipment-panel">
        <div>
          <div class="dd-equipment-name">LZ-1325 CNC Router<br>Event Decoration Configuration</div>
          <p class="dd-copy">
            A practical CNC router setup for event decoration workshops processing foam board, printed panels, decorative boards, and customized display components.
